     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h2>
  <p>The purpose of this document is to describe steps to deploy the RKE2 Kubernetes Distribution in High Availability with Nginx/HAProxy.</p>
  <h2 id="id-(4.3)RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-Pre-requisites"><span id="RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-Pre-requisites"></span>Pre-requisites&nbsp;
   <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
    <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/rke2-deployment-in-high-availability-with-nginx-ha#id-(4.3)RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-Pre-requisites">
