     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h2>
  <p>The prerequisites and cluster topologies are describe in the <a href="/cx/4.3/rke2-high-availability-pre-deployment-installati-1" data-scope="internal">RKE2 High Availability Pre-Deployment &amp; Installation Guide</a>. Please review the document before proceeding with installation in High Availability&nbsp;mode.</p>
