     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h2>
  <p>Decide what level of Availability is needed and prepare your nodes according to the below given structure for the solution</p>
  <h3 id="id-(4.3)RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-CIMPrerequisites"><span id="RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-CIMPrerequisites"></span>CIM Prerequisites&nbsp;
