    <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/rke2-deployment-in-high-availability-with-nginx-ha#id-(4.3)RKE2DeploymentinHighAvailabilityWithNginx/HAProxy-CIMPrerequisites">
